移动它们。

195
00:09:46,040 --> 00:09:49,880
All right, so when you're talking about a busy schedule, this means that you have lots
好的，所以当你说“繁忙的日程”时，这意味着你有很多

196
00:09:49,880 --> 00:09:52,280
