So nannies are usually hired on a contract basis.
所以保姆通常是按合同雇佣的。

245
00:12:16,640 --> 00:12:22,240
You say, I need a nanny to come and watch my kids every day, Monday to Friday for the
你会说，我需要一个保姆每天来照看我的孩子，从周一到周五，持续

246
